Package org.identityconnectors.framework.api

Class ResultsHandlerConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.identityconnectors.framework.api.ResultsHandlerConfiguration
  • public class ResultsHandlerConfiguration
extends Object
    SPI search operation has a default ResultsHandler-chain as:
    • NormalizingResultsHandler
    • FilteredResultsHandler
    • AttributesToGetSearchResultsHandler
    This configuration allow to overconfigure the chain.

    1.1
